Class ExcessReportPanel

java.lang.Object
ExcessReportPanel
public class ExcessReportPanel extends Object
Provides a panel to visualize excess ingredients based on a specified date and time. Users input a date and time, and the panel displays ingredients with more than 90% original inventory remaining since the given date and time.
